title: 4 Rare 80s Albums [Part 60] New Wave, Dark Wave
description:
These are four of my recent listens I have enjoyed a lot, hope you enjoy them too. It's just insane how many good records were released just between 1979 and 1984. It's more insane how most of them were totally shelved and overlooked.


Autumn Cathedral - Asleep Within Waves [1989]

Die Unbekannten - Don't Tell Me Stories [1983]

They Must Be Russians - & Other Groundless Accusations [1985]

Vector - Mannequin Virtue [1983]
